  <div class="c-entry-hero__header-wrap">
    <h1 class="c-page-title">How Medium became the best and worst place for coronavirus news</h1>

    
  </div>
  <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">The platform empowers voices — and misinformation  </p>

  
    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
        By
        <span class="c-byline__item">
          
            
            <a href="https://www.theverge.com/authors/zoe-schiffer" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Zoe Schiffer</span></a><span class="c-byline__item"><a href="https://www.twitter.com/ZoeSchiffer" class="c-byline__twitter-handle">@ZoeSchiffer</a></span>
          
